  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">2019 Iraq Crisis Funding Appeal - Displacement Tracking Matrix (DTM) in Iraq</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Through this project, IOM is providing access to up-to-date, reliable and comprehensive information about internally displaced persons and returnee populations in Iraq, as well as their needs and vulnerabilities. This is being achieved through the implementation of the Displacement Tracking Matrix (DTM) and timely dissemination of its results to government authorities, UN Humanitarian Country Team partners, NGOs, think tanks, media, academics and other relevant stakeholders. Through this project, IOM aims at increasing access to displacement information through the distribution of DTM products, enhancing regional and national government authorities&#x2019; data management capacities and improving access to data for clusters, including protection data to relevant cluster partners, and other relevant parties.</narrative>
  </description>
